From within a cold dark haze Ilsamore thought he heard Siofra's voice. But his mind and body were too battered to register the very real fact that it was indeed Siofra's voice he had heard. He surmised that it was his mind trying to free itself from the horrors of the place and, logically, it was reliving moments with Siofra. <br>
