<br>
&quot;Ye new te da area?&quot; Siofra jumped as the norseman appeared out of nowhere beside her. &quot;Sorry I startled ye.&quot; <br>
<br>
&quot;It be ok. I wasn' payin attention.&quot; Siofra motioned towards the children with her chin. &quot;Who'r dey? Dey don' look mos norse.&quot; <br>
<br>
&quot;Dat be cuz dey aren' yer evryday norse. Dose be da whelps of Vorsa. Ye really mus be new te da area if ye don' know dem. Dey be half-breeds. Der ma's an elf.&quot; Siofra tried to hide her interest as he continued to talk. &quot;Vorsa dun fell in luv wit one'a Ggorolut's slaves. She wa' jus a shell when Vorsa bot her from Ggorolut. Venchally she came round bu' she got no past. Members nuttin from fore Vorsa took er in.&quot; <br>
