&quot;I messed up didn't I?&quot; Ilsamore asked her, his voice was weak and strained. Just the action of forcing air out of his lungs to speak made his ribs hurt.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#A0B0E0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bkelrycksdaocradioandroleplaycenter.showUserPublicProfile?gid=vestachasiofra>VestachaSiofra</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Beloved lil Elf</span><br>  Posts: 87<br> <font color=#3333ff>(4/6/03 4:27:08 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fkelrycksdaocradioandroleplaycenterfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=82.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Into the Wolf's Den</span><hr size=1> Siofra stirred at the sound of Ilsamore's voice. Tears sprang to her eyes as she looked up at him. <br>
