<br>
&quot;She won't be coming back with us though.....&quot; she said, her voice strained. <br>
<br>
Ilsamore reached out towards Siofra again. <br>
<br>
He did not know the fate of Tshaya but knew, from the look on Siofra's face that she was not dead, or in pain. But Siofra did not look like she wanted to talk about it, so he left it at that.<br>
<br>
